elements.name: dispositionTypeCode
elements.description:
An indication as to CBP’s final disposition of action requested.

  • Not a final disposition record.
  • Final disposition; the transaction has been ACCEPTED by CBP; the action requested was successfully performed.
  • Final disposition; the transaction has been REJECTED by CBP; the action requested was NOT performed.

options.A: Final disposition; the transaction has been ACCEPTED by CBP; the action requested was successfully performed.
options.R: Final disposition; the transaction has been REJECTED by CBP; the action requested was NOT performed.

elements.name: severityCode
elements.description:
An indication as to the severity of the condition (if any):

  • ‘Fatally’ invalid data or critical error.
  • Census warning.
  • Partner Government Agency warning.
  • Informational notice ONLY.
  • No condition(s) encountered.

elements.name: conditionCode
elements.description: Code that identifies the condition or final disposition regarding an Entry Summary filing.

elements.name: reasonCode
elements.description: A further identification of the condition for CBP internal use ONLY.

elements.name: narrativeText
elements.description: Text description that corresponds to the Condition Code.

elements.name: entryFilerCode
elements.description: Filer’s identification code as reported on the input 10-Record.

elements.name: filler1
elements.description: Space fill. Reserved filler for possible future expansion of Entry Filer Code and/or Entry Number.

elements.name: entryNumber
elements.description: Unique identifying number assigned to the Entry by the Filer as reported on the input 10-Record.

elements.name: versionNumber
elements.description:
The latest version number of the entry summary (when the transaction is accepted).

The first 3 positions indicate the “major” revision number; the last 2 positions indicate the “minor” revision number.

elements.name: brokerReferenceNumber
elements.description: Conditionally, the Filer/Preparer’s internal Entry Summary identifier as reported on the input, if any.

elements.name: filler2
elements.description: Space fill until expanded length fully supported. Reserved filler for future expansion of the Broker Reference Number when fully ACE compatible.
